a Lipa|date=2018-02-23|work=Dua Lipa|access-date=2018-10-28}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:11em;\"|Date\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13em;\"|City\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10em;\"|Country\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20em;\"|Venue\n|-\n|6 July 2018{{efn|The concert of 6 July 2018 in Trelaze is part of [[NRJ in the Park]] festival.}}\n|[[Tr\u00e9laz\u00e9]]\n|France\n|Parc du Vissior\n|-\n|7 July 2018{{efn|The concert of 7 July 2018 in Roskilde is part of [[Rosklide]] festival.}}\n|[[Roskilde]]\n|Denmark\n|Darupvej\n|-\n|8 July 2018{{efn|The concert of 8 July 2018 in Turku is part of [[Ruisrock]] festival.}}\n|[[Turku]]\n|Finland\n|[[Ruissalo]]\n|-\n|12 July 2018{{efn|The concert of 12 July 2018 in Larvik is part of [[Stavernfestivalen]] festival.}}\n|[[Larvik]]\n|Norway\n|Larvik Golf Arena\n|-\n|14 July 2018{{efn|The concert of 14 July 2018 in Madrid is part of [[MadCool]] festival.}}\n|[[Madrid]]\n|[[Spain]]\n|[[Valdebebas]]\n|-\n|21 July 2018{{efn|The concert of 21 July 2018 in Boom is part of [[Tomorrowland]].}}\n|[[Boom, Belgium|Boom]]\n|Belgium\n|Recreation Area de Schorre\n|-\n|22 July 2018{{efn|The concert of 22 July 2018 in Paris is part of [[Lollapalooza Paris]].}}\n|Paris\n|France\n|[[Longchamp Racecourse|Hipodrome de Longchamp]]\n|}\n\n==== North American leg (27 July \u2013 5 August 2018) ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+List of tour dates with date, city, country, venue<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dualipa.com/2018-summer-festivals/|title=2018 Summer Festivals!! - Dua Lipa|date=2018-02-23|work=Dua Lipa|access-date=2018-10-28}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:11em;\"|Date\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13em;\"|City\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10em;\"|Country\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20em;\"|Venue\n|-\n|27 July 2018{{efn|This concert, scheduled for 27 July 2018, was cancelled due to rain and was due to be part of [[Panorama Music Festival]].}}\n|New York City\n|United State