17-2018)|The Self-Titled Tour]]<br>(2017\u201318)\n| this_tour ='''Future Nostalgia Tour'''<br>(2021)\n| next_tour = \n}}\nThe '''Future Nostalgia Tour''' is the fifth concert tour by English singer Dua Lipa. The tour will support her second studio album, [[Future Nostalgia (Dua Lipa album)|''Future Nostalgia'']] (2020). Originally planned to take place in spring-summer 2020, the tour was postponed to early 2021 due to the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].<ref name=\"livenation\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.livenation.co.uk/artist/dua-lipa-tickets|title=Dua Lipa Tickets|last=|first=|date=24 March 2020|website=[[Live Nation]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324104559/https://www.livenation.co.uk/artist/dua-lipa-tickets|archive-date=24 March 2020|access-date=24 March 2020}}</ref>\n=== Tour dates ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+List of concerts, showing date, city, country, venue, opening acts, tickets sold, number of available tickets and gross revenue<ref>Dates:\n\n*Original: {{Cite web|url=https://www.dualipa.com/tour/|title=Tour - Dua Lipa|last=|first=|date=12 February 2020|website=dualipa.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200214173234/https://www.dualipa.com/tour/|archive-date=14 February 2020|access-date=14 February 2020}}\n*Rescheduled: {{Cite web|url=https://www.livenation.co.uk/artist/dua-lipa-tickets|title=Dua Lipa Tickets|last=|first=|date=24 March 2020|website=[[Live Nation]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324104559/https://www.livenation.co.uk/artist/dua-lipa-tickets|archive-date=24 March 2020|access-date=24 March 2020}}\n</ref><ref>Opening acts:\n*Lolo Zoua\u00ef and DJ Buck Betty: {{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/DUALIPA/status/1216725081860251650|title=Taking my girlfriendsssss on TOUR!!! We\u2019re excited to see youuuuu|last=Lipa|first=Dua|date=13 January 2020|via=[[Twitter]]|access-date=13 January 2020}}\n*Dagny: {{