{"title_page": "The Death Triangle", "text_new": "{{Infobox wrestling team||article_name=The Death Triangle|type=S|image=The Death Triangle logo.png|caption=The Death Triangle logo|members=[[Pac (wrestler)|Pac]]<br>[[Pentag\u00f3n Jr.]]<br>[[Fenix (wrestler)|Rey Fenix]]|names='''The Death Triangle'''|heights=Pac: {{height|ft=5|in=8}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cagematch.net/?id=2&nr=3497|title=Pac|publisher=Cagematch|website=Cagematch.net|accessdate=March 11, 2019}}</ref><br>Pentagon: {{height|ft=5|in=11}}<ref name=\"Pentagon Jr\">{{cite web|url=hhttps://www.cagematch.net/?id=2&nr=10334|title=Pentagon Jr |publisher=Cagematch|website=Cagematch.net|accessdate=September 4, 2019}}</ref><br>Fenix: {{height|ft=5|in=10}}<ref name=\"Rey Fenix\">{{cite web|url=https://www.cagematch.net/?id=2&nr=10343|title=Rey Fenix |publisher=Cagematch|website=Cagematch.net|accessdate=September 4, 2019}}</ref>|weights={{convert|559|lb|kg|abbr=on}}|debut=4 March 2020|disbanded=|years_active=2020\u2013present}}'''The Death Triangle''' are a professional wrestling stable, currently performing in [[All Elite Wrestling]] (AEW). Led by \"The Bastard\" [[Pac (wrestler)|Pac]], the stable consists of [[Pentag\u00f3n Jr.]] and [[F\u00e9nix (wrestler)|Rey Fenix]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lastwordonprowrestling.com/2020/03/05/aew-dynamite-death-triangle/|title=AEW Dynamite Highlights - PAC, Lucha Bros Form Death Triangle (3/4/20)|last=Edwards|first=Scott|date=2020-03-05|website=Last Word on Pro Wrestling|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>\n\n== Professional wrestling career ==\n\n=== All Elite Wrestling (2020-present) ===\n[[File:Neville2017.jpg|thumb|[[Pac (wrestler)|Pac]], leader of the stable]]\nOn 4 March 2020, when Pac defeated Chuck Taylor, Trent came to confront Pac. Then Orange Cassidy went face to face with Pac. Rey Fenix and Pentagon Jr came to the ring and super kicked Orange Cassidy. Pac took the mic and introduced his new stable known as the Death Triangle.<ref>{{Cite web